===Background===

Naath is a frequent target of slaving raids from [[Slaver's Bay]], which is in [[Essos]] on the opposite northern side of the Summer Sea.

Missandei's village was attacked and burned by slavers when she was five years old, and she was captured and taken to the slaver-city of [[Astapor]].&lt;ref name=&quot;S04E04&quot;&gt;&quot;[[Oathkeeper]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

===[[Season 4]]===

Missandei recalls to [[Grey Worm]] that she is from an island called Naath, and was taken by the slavers when she was five years old.&lt;ref name=&quot;S04E04&quot;/&gt;
